  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onions and cook until they start to brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the bulghur wheat and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the potatoes and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the garlic sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with salt, black pepper, and red pepper flakes to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
